# Protection rules
- Never modify files matching these globs unless the user explicitly writes: ALLOW PROTECTED EDITS.
- If a change requires touching a protected file, STOP and propose a plan listing exact paths and diffs.
- Do not rename or move protected files.
- Prefer additive work elsewhere; then ask to proceed.